    {
      "name": "4. Zero-Latency Verification",
      "description": "Requests to verify the Zero-Latency Table Synchronization system. \n\nNote: For real-time testing, use the `scripts/test-socket-hold.html` tool to observe the `tableStatusChanged` socket events.",
